line_1: Observ'd a rock, which o'er a castle lean'd;
line_2: The Bactrians this were careless to defend,

line_1: But pensive PATCH, who on the window lean'd;
line_2: No well-dress'd youth in coffee-house remain'd,

line_1: Cross-armed and back to wall poor William leant.
line_2: Where o'er an earthen seat the thorn is bent,
